    <p>{`A solution is to use IIS instead of IIS Express. This way, every compilation, only the libraries that has changed are compiled but once it is compiled, all your system will stay in a working stage (indeed it must have been in a working stage). To switch is pretty easy. Open IIS and create one website for your web project and so on. Define different ports for all your website and that's it. Not so fast! You can have a error 500:`}</p>
